<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">My understanding (and correct me if I'm wrong, as experience seems to bear this out) is that wisdom and intelligence both affect trade skills, but in different ways.  My understanding:  Wisdom has an affect on how successful you are in producing the desired item, and intelligence has an affect on how fast you go up in trade skills levels.<p>

