<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">http://eq.castersrealm.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=2378<p>

This link contains the DEFINATIVE answer right from an EQ designer.<p>

The fact is the higher of EITHER wis or int is applied as a modifier to trade skills.<p>

So in your case, your WIS will help you, and your low INT shouldn't affect you in a negative way.<p>

Hope this help,<br>
